  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Alternate Cost: 5 Chakra</p><p>When you cast a Ninjutsu that deals damage, and can only target one creature you create an echo of the jutsu. </p><p>You can cast the same ninjutsu of the same rank, using your bonus action on the following turn without spending chakra. </p><p>The jutsu's echo only deals half damage. </p><p>The jutsu's echo must target the same creature.</p>",
